title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 10' game
maintext:
ALBANY, N.Y. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Sunday evening’s drawing of the New York Lottery’s “Pick 10” game were:
01-06-07-08-10-20-21-26-27-28-40-43-45-46-47-60-62-65-68-72
(one, six, seven, eight, ten, twenty, twenty-one, twenty-six, twenty-seven, twenty-eight, forty, forty-three, forty-five, forty-six, forty-seven, sixty, sixty-two, sixty-five, sixty-eight, seventy-two)
